12 March 2009Communicators of the Justice, Crime Prevention and Security (JCPS) cluster will host a networking session with the members of the media that are covering issues under the cluster.Media are invited to the networking session as follows:Venue: Indaba Hotel, Fourways Date: Friday, 13 March 2009 Time: 17h30 for 18h00Media interested in attending the session should RSVP with: Piwe Mbiko Cell: 079 505 9713 E-mail: mbikop@saps.org.za by midday (12h00) on Friday, 13 March 2009.Enquiries Piwe Mbiko Cell: 079 505 9713Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS) on behalf of JCPS Cluster